      "message": "I find this comment very confusing.  If a frame is restore_previous it won\u0027t be used again so why shouldn\u0027t we overwrite it?\n\nIf a frame is restore_previous it will not be use again, therefore we should not ever overwrite fRestoreFrame with a frame tagged as restore_previous.",
