        "id": 5255
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-01-12T15:42:46Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Because the following frame may depend on fActiveFrame. We have the following frames:\n\ni - 1: Currently stored in fActiveFrame. Let\u0027s say it\u0027s KEEP\ni    : About to decode into fActiveFrame.  This is RESTORE_PREVIOUS and independent\ni + 1: This frame may depend on i - 1\n\nWhen it comes time to decode |i + 1|, we want to start with |i - 1|, rather than having to go back further.",
      "parentUuid": "9b382592_3820b0ef",
